Module for limiting access to admin pages per IP

add these to settings.php and modify to follow your needs:

# regex list for path limit
$conf['ip_acl_paths'] = array("/^admin/i","/^user/i","/^node\/+.*\/+edit/i", "/^node\/+add/i");

# list of allowed IPs
$conf['ip_acl_ips'] = array('127.0.0.1', '194.90.1.5');

# A nasty error message to present
$conf['ip_acl_error'] = "Error";
